{"lemma":"فَعّالٌ","slug":"فَعّالٌ","root":"ف.ع.ل","root_slug":"ف-ع-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/ف-ع-ل","pos":"ADJ","pos_camel":"adj","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"فَعّال","root":"فعل","pos":"N","occurrence_count":2},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["adj","noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":4},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n34205","n34206","n34207","n34209"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%81%D9%8E%D8%B9%D9%91%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"who does things or realizes them; effecting","examples":[{"text":"وَهُوَ الْغَفُورُ الْوَدُودُ / ذُو الْعَرْشِ الْمَجِيدُ / فَعَّالٌ لِّمَا يُرِيدُ","english":"And He is the Most-Forgiving, the Most-Loving, / Of the Throne, the Glorious, / Effecting what He wills."}]},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"that causes effects; affecting; active"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"that causes effects; affecting; active; effective; effectual; efficacious"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"plural of فِعْل (fiʕl)","tags":["form-of","plural"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/faʕ.ʕaːl/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n34205","headword_ar":"فَعَالٌ","root":"fEl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nazaAli","text_ar":"نَزَالِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", has sometimes occurred as meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AifoEalo","text_ar":"اِفْعَلْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Do thou"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (O, K. *)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n34206","headword_ar":"فَعَالٌ","root":"fEl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (O, K,) accord. to Lth, (O,) is a name for"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A good doing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"such as"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"liberality,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bounty,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"generosity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K, [the only meaning assigned to it in the S,]) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like of these:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O:) or, (O, K,) accord. to IAar, (O,) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"doing of a single person,"},{"kind":"text","text":"peculiarly, [as distinguished from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiEaAlN","text_ar":"فِعَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.,] (O,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"relating to good"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to evil;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K;) one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN kariymu AlfaEaAli","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ كَرِيمُ الفَعَالِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one is generous in respect of doing"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"doings"},{"kind":"text","text":"], and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN lay^iymu AlfaEaAli","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ لَيِيمُ الفَعَالِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one is mean in respect of doing"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"doings"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (O: [and the like is said in the T and in the Msb;]) and Az says that this is the correct explanation: not that of Lth; and Mbr [likewise] says, it is used in commendation and in discommendation: (O:) and it is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"used only of a single agent."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K.) ―         -b2-  It is also an inf. n. (S, O, Msb. [See 1, first sentence.])"}],"source_refs":["O","K"]},{"entry_id":"n34207","headword_ar":"فِعَالٌ","root":"fEl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", as distinguished from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEaAlN","text_ar":"فَعَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A doing that is between two"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"agents"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (IAar, O, K, TA;) and therefore it is an inf. n. of ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faAEala","text_ar":"فَاعَلَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[a verb of which I have not found any ex.]. (TA.) ―         -b2-  It is also a pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiEolN","text_ar":"فِعْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, O, Msb, K.       -A2-  Also The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"handle,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"piece of wood that is inserted into the hole,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, IB, O,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the axe,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"adz,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hoe:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, IB, O, K:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fuEulN","text_ar":"فُعُلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.)"}],"source_refs":["K","IAar","IB","O"]},{"entry_id":"n34209","headword_ar":"فَعَّالٌ","root":"fEl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Wont to do"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Kur xi. 109 and lxxxv. 16. [Thus in the phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faE~aAlN limaA yuriydu","text_ar":"فَعَّالٌ لِمَا يُرِيدُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Wont to do what He willeth:"},{"kind":"text","text":"relating to God.])"}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}